1.0.name: wordpress/tuned
1.0.description: Tuned Theme is a simple responsive full width theme for WordPress. The translation ready responsive Tuned theme looks good on any devices(mobile, tablet, nootebook, PC...). Supports custom menus, cudtom header, custom background, RTL languages and the following extras: Hero Unit, Carousel, Infinite Scroll Blog, Front Page Template.
